title: Model Test Program
description: 3 Month model test program that includes all subjects for board exams. We follow board standard system and board sysllabus.

title: SSC/HSC Program
description: This program is for SSC/HSC candidate students. We will teach students to complete the board standard syllabus and prepare them for the board exam.

title: PEC/JSC program
description: This program is for PEC/JSC candidate students. We will teach students to complete the board standard syllabus and prepare them for the board exam.

title: Admission Test
description: Admission test program for the HSC students those are completed their HSC board exam. We are ready to prepare you for the University admission test.

title: Home Tutor
description: We provide home tutor if anyone needed. We have large number of qualified teachers collection for each and every subjects.

title: Individual Subject Program
description: Sometimes student needs specific subjects lessons. So we have this service for these type of students. We want to provide the best service all the time.

title: Group Subject Program
description: We have Science, Business Studies and also for the Humanities group subject program. We make different batch for the different groups students.

title: Special Objective Test
description: We have huge objective test program. So that student can practice objective tests. This is very important for the students.

title: Monthly Exam
description: In our regular academic programs we take monthly exam each every month so that we can realize students progress.

title: Academic Syllabus Program
description: We follow the academic syllabus so that student can do well in their academic exams. If they need extra class we also provide it.

title: Special Batch Program
description: Special batch program is specially for the female students those want to only with girls. On the other side we also provide same institute batch.

title: Practical Class Program
description: We provide practical classes so that student and also provide multimedia class when needed.
